parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power or acceleration
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or becomes stuck in gear
the transmission makes a loud clicking or grinding noise
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the vehicle will not move forward or backward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power or acceleration
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or becomes stuck in gear
the torque converter makes a loud grinding or whining noise
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the vehicle will not move forward or backward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electronic issues can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electronic systems malfunction
the vehicle's warning lights illuminate
the vehicle's systems behave erratically
the vehicle's systems fail to respond to driver input.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion of Third-Row Seat Latch and Wheel Well
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the third-row seat latch and wheel well can cause the seat to become detached, leading to accidents or injuries, and also allow water to enter the vehicle, causing damage to electrical components and compromising safety.
symptoms: The third-row seat latch or striker corrodes
the seat becomes detached or falls out
water enters the vehicle through the wheel well
rust or mold is visible under the seat or in the wheel well
the seat does not latch properly
the seat leans forward or becomes unstable.
